```

Anti_Pattern.Good:
```typescript
rules: {
    'no-unused-vars': 'off',
    '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars': 'off',
    'no-undef': 'off',
    'consistent-return': 'off',
}
// The npm "typecheck" script runs tsc --noEmit and is the authoritative gate for these.
```
